etchHTTP =3D (ComplexType) (settingshandler.getModule
("HTTP"));

ComplexTy=
pe fetchHTTP =3D (ComplexType)
(settingshandler.getComplexTypeByAbsoluteNam=
e
(settingshandler.getSettings(null), "/crawl-order/fetch-
processors/HTTP"=
));
